{"title":"Ass Savers+Gramm Detour Cloud Cap brings shade wherever bikepacking adventure leads","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/19/ass-saversgramm-detour-cloud-cap-brings-shade-wherever-bikepacking-adventure-leads/","date":1629410487000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The new Detour Cloud Cap collaboration between Ass Savers &amp; Gramm Tourpacking is as simply functional as it is niche – a cycling cap with a built-in neck scarf to protect you from the unrelenting sun. Some days on the bike there’s really just no escape from the sun. And since Ass Savers &amp; Gramm couldn’t find the cap they wanted, they decided to make their own and share it with the bikepacking world…</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" data-ezsrc=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/582965651\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\" ezoid=\"0.6192854394700957\"></iframe></p><p>Sure, most cyclists will make do fine with some sunscreen to protect the back of the neck &amp; ears on sunny rides. But if you are setting off on a multi-day adventure bikepacking ride or race where you may be out, fully exposed in the hot sun for days or weeks at a time – like at the <a href=\"https://www.silkroadmountainrace.cc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Silk Road Mountain Race</a> that is crossing Kyrgyzstan right now, or the <a href=\"https://atlasmountainrace.cc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Atlas Mountain Race</a> across Morocco in October – it’s hard to beat a headcloth.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top.jpg\" alt=\"Detour Cloud Cap hot weather adventure bikepacking cycling cap sun protection by Ass Savers &amp; Gramm Tourpacking,&nbsp;top\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_top-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144847/Detour-Cl