or.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19145356/Detour-Cloud-Cap_SRMR-Toms-Alsbergs-helmet-696x371.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19145356/Detour-Cloud-Cap_SRMR-Toms-Alsbergs-helmet-1068x570.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19145356/Detour-Cloud-Cap_SRMR-Toms-Alsbergs-helmet-788x420.jpg 788w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-268821\">c. Ass Savers, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tomsalsbergs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Toms Alsbergs</a> at SRMR now</figcaption></figure><p>The Detour Cloud Cap is made to be worn on its own or under a helmet. The 34cm long rear neck shade has a slick satin inner finish that’s meant to be soft sliding &amp; flapping against your skin. Without a helmet, it’s light enough to move in the breeze. Under helmet straps, you’ll likely need to pull it away from or over your ears to keep air moving.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144841/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_bottom.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144841/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_bottom.jpg\" alt=\"Detour Cloud Cap hot weather adventure bikepacking cycling cap sun protection by Ass Savers &amp; Gramm Tourpacking,&nbsp;bottom\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144841/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_bottom.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144841/Detour-