cling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_bottom-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144841/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_bottom-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a></p><p>But the idea like a traditional desert headcloth is to both allowing airflow and also keep your sweat from evaporating too quickly so you stay cooler and slow down dehydration under the hot sun.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144833/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_front-to-back.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144833/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_front-to-back.jpg\" alt=\"Detour Cloud Cap hot weather adventure bikepacking cycling cap sun protection by Ass Savers &amp; Gramm Tourpacking,&nbsp;front &amp; back\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144833/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_front-to-back.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144833/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_front-to-back-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/19144833/Detour-Cloud-Cap-hot-weather-adventure-bikepacking-cycling-cap-sun-protection-by-Ass-Savers-and-Gramm-Tourpacking_front-to-back-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amaz